### Multilingual API Examples
### This file contains example HTTP requests for testing the multilingual functionality

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@projectId = 507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
@categoryId = 507f1f77bcf86cd799439012

### 1. Create a Category (Multilingual)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": {
    "en": "Technology",
    "ar": "تكنولوجيا"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "Technology related projects",
    "ar": "مشاريع متعلقة بالتكنولوجيا"
  },
  "isActive": true
}

### 2. Create a Project (Multilingual)
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": {
    "en": "E-commerce Website",
    "ar": "موقع تجارة إلكترونية"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "A full-stack e-commerce platform with modern UI/UX",
    "ar": "منصة تجارة إلكترونية متكاملة مع واجهة مستخدم حديثة"
  },
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "isActive": true
}

### 3. Get All Categories in English (Default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

### 4. Get All Categories in Arabic (Query Parameter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?lang=ar

### 5. Get All Categories in Arabic (Accept-Language Header)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Accept-Language: ar-SA,ar;q=0.9,en;q=0.8

### 6. Get All Projects in English
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects

### 7. Get All Projects in Arabic (Query Parameter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?lang=ar

### 8. Get All Projects in Arabic (Accept-Language Header)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects
Accept-Language: ar

### 9. Get Single Category in English
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}

### 10. Get Single Category in Arabic
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}?lang=ar

### 11. Get Single Project in English
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}

### 12. Get Single Project in Arabic
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}?lang=ar

### 13. Get Active Categories in English
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/active

### 14. Get Active Categories in Arabic
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/active?lang=ar

### 15. Update Category (Multilingual)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": {
    "en": "Web Development",
    "ar": "تطوير الويب"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "Web development and design projects",
    "ar": "مشاريع تطوير وتصميم المواقع"
  }
}

### 16. Update Project (Multilingual)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": {
    "en": "Modern E-commerce Platform",
    "ar": "منصة تجارة إلكترونية حديثة"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "A comprehensive e-commerce solution with advanced features",
    "ar": "حل تجارة إلكترونية شامل مع ميزات متقدمة"
  }
}

